@Node "catalogs" "CDpro/your own catalog"
@Next "Main"
@Prev "Main"
@Toc  "Main"

With CDproV3.5 you can write catalogs in your own language. All files you
need, you can find in the directory "CDpro/catalogs/deutsch". Use an editor
with more than 620 columns (Black Editor, GoldED,...). I take FlexCat to
create the catalog file (Aminet: dev/misc)

Send me your catalog file (or installer script) with source or upload it
to Aminet: biz/dbase/ (use the version (like V3.5) in the filename...)

All descriptions in this manual using the english defaults from CDpro...

special thanx...
@EndNode




